r.com.au Dick Johnson Racing official website]\n*[http://www.icmi.com.au/dick-johnson Dick Johnson's Elaborated Biography]\n*[http://racing-reference.info/driver/Dick_Johnson_(2) Racing Reference profile (US stats)]\n*[http://www.driverdb.com/drivers/dick-johnson/ Driver Database profile]\n\n<BR>\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Peter Brock]] <br> [[Jim Richards (race driver)|Jim Richards]] | title = Winner of the [[Bathurst 1000]] | years = [[1981 James Hardie 1000|1981]] <br> (with [[John French (racing driver)|John French]]) | after = [[Peter Brock]] <br> [[Larry Perkins]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Peter Brock]] | title = Winner of the [[Australian Touring Car Championship]] | years = [[1981 Australian Touring Car Championship|1981]] & [[1982 Australian Touring Car Championship|1982]] | after = [[Allan Moffat]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Allan Moffat]] | title = Winner of the [[Australian Touring Car Championship]] | years = [[1984 Australian Touring Car Championship|1984]] | after = [[Jim Richards (race driver)|Jim Richards]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Jim Richards (race driver)|Jim Richards]] | title = Winner of the [[Australian Touring Car Championship]] | years = [[1988 Australian Touring Car Championship|1988]] & [[1989 Australian Touring Car Championship|1989]] | after = [[Jim Richards (race driver)|Jim Richards]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Tony Longhurst]] <br> [[Tomas Mezera]] | title = Winner of the [[Bathurst 1000]] | years = [[1989 Tooheys 1000|1989]] <br> (with [[John Bowe (racing driver)|John Bowe]]) | after = [[Allan Grice]] <br> [[Win Percy]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Larry Perkins]] <br> [[Gregg Hansford]] | title = Winner of the [[Bathurst 1000]] | years = [[1994 Tooheys 1000|1994]] <br> (with [[John Bowe (racing driver)|John Bowe]]) | after = [[Larry Perkins]] <br> [[Russell Ingall]]}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Gregg Hansford]] <br> [[Neil Crompton]] | title = [[Bathurst 12 Hour|Winne